{"tid":1293043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又和平散水？咁同民陣同泛民班政棍有咩分別呀？","createTime":"2019-07-07T14:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T14:37:48.000Z","uid":122994,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9793107f96e76b945f7928e6dd90205a7113c7a6","tid":1293043,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好撚大分別呀！屌你老味！</span><br />\n<br />\n以前泛民班友下下講到end game咁call人出黎，遊行完之後<br />\n<br />\n1. 無後續抗爭路線圖<br />\n2. 無行動升級plan<br />\n3. 永遠唔設死線<br />\n4. 話階級性勝利比掌聲自己<br />\n<br />\n永遠只係睇住d大白象同法案過，口講譴責，但不升級，但不設死線，不停&ldquo;監察&rdquo;。當有人想做其他野時，佢地<br />\n<br />\n1. 話信唔過叫人唔好去<br />\n2. 篤灰<br />\n3. 割蓆<br />\n<br />\n呢d就叫大台呀，呢d就叫鳩行呀，大家以為見到有咁既行動模式一樣要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，咁我地今日行完之後有無後續行動plan呀？好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 擠提<br />\n2. 接力遊行<br />\n3. 反紅媒<br />\n4. 光復行動<br />\n5. 714法革記念日聲援天琦<br />\n<br />\n差唔多咩撚都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁點會係鳩行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚明顯就係為之後既行動集氣同給予正當性wo？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話鳩行果d係咪泛民打手以前比人屌得多要屌返人平衡下呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e488fa05390ece00090f6c3ee8099faba984f712","tid":1293043,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fb07cde884d88093bbc18bd3cf3aea3ec58fb5f","tid":1293043,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"772107c319e7f0065dde61ee2c6c3d201e295718","tid":1293043,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7685fda5f9f8de96e58f23f4af8e7acf99a6d600","tid":1293043,"uid":1229